Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.93,0:00:02.39,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,There, they've rounded the final corner...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.40,0:00:04.27,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,We're down to the last 200 meters!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.85,0:00:04.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.28,0:00:05.05,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Which horse will win?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.55,0:00:05.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.52,0:00:07.06,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Will it be the favorite, Iron Blade, in Lane 4?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.89,0:00:07.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, come on, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.40,0:00:09.77,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Or, maybe even the trump in lane 2, Devil Typhoon?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.02,0:00:09.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, just a bit more...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.03,0:00:12.75,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,The outcome will depend on the fighting spirit of each horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.64,0:00:14.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For the sake of the Mouri Detective Agency's future!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.84,0:00:18.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Love is eternal, labyrinths are mysterious.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.04,0:00:19.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Saturday nights are for mystery!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.48,0:00:22.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The clue is a large scar!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.35,0:00:24.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Differentiate between the first love and the suspect!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.70,0:00:26.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perceiving the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.20,0:00:28.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The appearance of a child and the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.16,0:00:29.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.81,0:02:18.87,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Iron Blade in Lane 4 leads by a half-length...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.90,0:02:20.46,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Masked Yaiba in Lane isn't far behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.27,0:02:20.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.51,0:02:21.65,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,And Black Chaser in Lane 8 is close!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.68,0:02:22.52,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,And there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.56,0:02:24.19,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,We have one coming from behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.03,0:02:23.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.20,0:02:26.58,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Devil Typhoon! Devil Typhoon! It's Devil Typhoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.99,0:02:26.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, come on, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.60,0:02:27.34,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,It's over!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.38,0:02:29.34,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,The winner is Devil Typhoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.36,0:02:31.50,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,What an unexpected outcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.24,0:02:31.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Finally!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.52,0:02:32.81,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,The crowd is in an uproar!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.08,0:02:33.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.66,0:02:35.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You won?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.04,0:02:36.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.12,0:02:37.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The three million jackpot!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.21,0:02:39.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Three million!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.67,0:02:41.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dear, God!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.34,0:02:43.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you for watching over this detective agency!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.92,0:02:46.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Especially during this particularly difficult month!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.83,0:02:49.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's because we practically had no cases this month...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.84,0:02:50.94,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Please hold on...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.95,0:02:52.56,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,The judge's deliberation lamp has been lit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.71,0:02:55.14,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Was there a problem in the scramble to the finish?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.42,0:02:57.59,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.60,0:03:00.32,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Devil Typhoon in Lane 2 has been disqualified for stepping out of lane.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.35,0:03:03.66,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,And now, the new order has the winner as Iron Blade from Lane 4!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.86,0:03:03.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,God!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.15,0:03:06.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haven't you always been on my side, buddy!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.20,0:03:11.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, recently...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.99,0:03:14.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was a rich lady...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.16,0:03:17.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who bought a lottery ticket on a whim and won 100 million yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.46,0:03:18.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was all over the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.87,0:03:19.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.13,0:03:23.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Moreover, she said she plans to give the winning ticket to someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.13,0:03:29.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems that, when she met with a traffic accident in her childhood...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.01,0:03:31.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A boy was seriously injured trying to protect her...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.43,0:03:35.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So she wanted to express her gratitude by giving\Nhim the 100 million, if he would come forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.06,0:03:36.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.98,0:03:39.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Has this lucky boy appeared?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.77,0:03:40.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.73,0:03:44.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the course of the accident, her eyes\Nwere damaged and she lost her sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.36,0:03:47.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since the boy was also a child then...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.44,0:03:50.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She wouldn't be able to identify him by his face or voice anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.78,0:03:51.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.91,0:03:54.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How does she intend to find that boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.74,0:03:57.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From the injury he sustained during the accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.75,0:03:59.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was a huge wound...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.33,0:04:02.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So even after growing into an adult, the scar would still be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.75,0:04:05.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow, I have a scar as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.80,0:04:10.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Two years ago —\hit's the scar from when I slid headfirst\Non the baseball field and injured the top of my shoulder!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.43,0:04:12.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you think there's any chance I can fake it!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.34,0:04:14.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Fake it"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.16,0:04:17.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, this old guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.85,0:04:19.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It wasn't on the shoulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.53,0:04:30.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was a straight tear across his T-shirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.53,0:04:33.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I clearly recall the blood seeping from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.37,0:04:38.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Afterwards, my eyesight began to deteriorate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.58,0:04:41.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That is the only image I cannot forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.58,0:04:44.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's this person—the 100 million yen...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.63,0:04:51.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, are you here to ask me to find\Nthat boy by using only the scar as a clue?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.63,0:04:53.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.38,0:04:56.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are people who have come forward claiming they are the one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.22,0:04:58.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In fact...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.64,0:05:00.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are two of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.35,0:05:02.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Two?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.85,0:05:05.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.06,0:05:12.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'd like for me to determine which of these two is the real one?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.03,0:05:12.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.49,0:05:16.41,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Shoudou Kurumi (39)\NHead of the Shoudou Family
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.87,0:05:16.41,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,The boy who saved me was just one person, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.03,0:05:18.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.12,0:05:19.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One of them is a fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.50,0:05:24.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone who would pretend to be the one from\Nthis kind lady's memory for the sake of money...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.75,0:05:26.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a shameless bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.75,0:05:28.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're one to talk...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.71,0:05:29.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.55,0:05:32.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you observe the scars on the two of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.13,0:05:35.72,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Houya Taisuke (40)\NButler
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.45,0:05:33.39,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.99,0:05:35.72,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Although I did see them...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.20,0:05:37.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.35,0:05:41.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The brown-haired man has it on his back, while...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.52,0:05:45.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The man with the dark complexion has one on his chest...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.73,0:05:47.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Both of them have very large scars.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.82,0:05:50.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the back and chest?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.61,0:05:54.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Miss, do you not know the location of the wound?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.82,0:05:56.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.03,0:06:00.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I only remember that it was severe and nearly went from side to side.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.24,0:06:03.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, where did the accident occur?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.87,0:06:05.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.42,0:06:07.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,During the summer holidays, some thirty years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.42,0:06:11.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It happened while I was on vacation with my parents in Izu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.01,0:06:16.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I met a boy around my age at the beach, and we became good friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.59,0:06:19.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,During the vacation, we played together every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.76,0:06:22.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was very familiar with the sea and the types of fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.02,0:06:25.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And he always drank ginger ale.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.81,0:06:29.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He looked so cute when I could see his white teeth\Ngleaming alongside his tanned face from time to time...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.02,0:06:31.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My, it was love at first sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.07,0:06:37.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, those dream-like days couldn't last for eternity...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.16,0:06:39.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the last day of the vacation...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.82,0:06:42.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I cried and told him, "I don't want to go home..."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.49,0:06:44.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Then, stay here..."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.79,0:06:47.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"I'll protect you," is what he said at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.25,0:06:50.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, how old were you at the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.63,0:06:53.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think I was in my second year of elementary school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.96,0:06:56.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This lovey-dovey even in the second year of elementary?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.34,0:06:59.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, how did the accident happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.18,0:07:05.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I selfishly petitioned for my parents to stay in Izu for one more day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.85,0:07:09.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I saw him walking on the road near\Nthe coastline, I tried to run up and tell him...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.27,0:07:10.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But just when I caught him...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.94,0:07:14.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A drowsy driver ended up veering toward the sidewalk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.95,0:07:21.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Afterwards, I was unconscious for three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.99,0:07:24.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I came to, I was already in a hospital bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.08,0:07:25.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.70,0:07:29.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't know what became of that boy after that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.21,0:07:31.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.29,0:07:33.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was told later that that boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.92,0:07:38.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Had carried me to the hospital with a large wound of his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.88,0:07:42.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He told the hospital staff that he would call for his parents and left...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.97,0:07:44.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But was never seen there again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.26,0:07:46.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.22,0:07:48.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You must have asked for his name, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.52,0:07:50.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I mean, you had been playing together for a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.77,0:07:52.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gari{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.36,0:07:57.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"My classmates refer to me as Gari, so\Nthat's what you can call me as well."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.49,0:07:59.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was the answer you gave on TV, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.74,0:08:00.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.95,0:08:03.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Gari" should be able to count as a name...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.99,0:08:04.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.87,0:08:07.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where are those two who came forward right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.79,0:08:10.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They've been staying at my house for the past two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.79,0:08:16.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a luxurious home!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.34,0:08:20.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I bet a place this big sure takes a while to get clean, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.01,0:08:22.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.09,0:08:25.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all due to the limitless effort of Houya{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and the two maids.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.97,0:08:29.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, since there are only four of us living here, including myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.10,0:08:32.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are rarely many places that need cleaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.85,0:08:35.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I bet the dusting is more than enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.36,0:08:37.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.28,0:08:39.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you say "four" people, does that mean your parents...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.07,0:08:42.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My mother passed away from illness some time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.36,0:08:46.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My father, who had taken care of me until his\Ndeath, fell ill and passed on three years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.45,0:08:49.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just prior to my father's passing...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.08,0:08:50.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He decided to hire this butler.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.79,0:08:54.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the one who took on the burden of caring for me, Houya{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.17,0:08:56.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.84,0:08:58.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's certainly no burden.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.55,0:09:02.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it seems we've added two more recently...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.84,0:09:04.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, with you, that will bring us to nine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.47,0:09:10.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I suppose we'll have quite a feast tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.40,0:09:15.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So good, so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.02,0:09:19.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As they say, the more the merrier when meals are concerned.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.28,0:09:20.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.74,0:09:26.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One of us here doesn't belong, and yet is getting a free meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.21,0:09:32.95,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0}Kasumoto Ryuuhei (42)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.36,0:09:31.52,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Don't you think it's best if you admit it already?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.62,0:09:32.95,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Impostor{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.30,0:09:37.29,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0}Banba Sougo (41)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.09,0:09:37.29,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I think I'm the one who should be saying just that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.54,0:09:39.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, we'll sort this out later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.46,0:09:42.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective Mouri will ascertain the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.88,0:09:44.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that not so, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.48,0:09:45.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.84,0:09:49.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll question them in the next room, individually, for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.47,0:09:52.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, Detective{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.23,0:09:56.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Until later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.44,0:09:58.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.73,0:10:01.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please do your best to differentiate between them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.49,0:10:05.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The possibility remains that both of them are impostors.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.15,0:10:05.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.20,0:10:08.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, it has been thirty years now...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.58,0:10:13.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's possible the boy has already passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.54,0:10:14.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.58,0:10:15.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.00,0:10:19.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have no doubt that he is in this house!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.09,0:10:20.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I refuse to think that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.63,0:10:24.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I specially requested the great\Ndetective, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, to investigate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.59,0:10:28.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems that I've grown a little tired...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.76,0:10:30.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll retreat to my room for some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.68,0:10:33.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Once you have reached your conclusion...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.56,0:10:35.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please come and reveal it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.77,0:10:38.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.32,0:10:47.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could that lady...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.32,0:10:50.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Already know which one is him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.37,0:10:52.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.08,0:10:52.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.33,0:10:55.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.79,0:10:57.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.67,0:11:00.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you see something outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.50,0:11:01.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't feel it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.04,0:11:03.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As if we were being watched...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.51,0:11:05.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.63,0:11:11.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not really feeling anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.52,0:11:18.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Afterward...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.52,0:11:22.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle inquired with the two of them\Nover the boy from thirty years ago, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.98,0:11:26.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The two of them only repeated the same answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.03,0:11:28.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, that was to be expected...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.45,0:11:29.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.70,0:11:34.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She mentioned everything about the situation in her TV interview?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.41,0:11:40.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The date of the accident, the model of the car, and\Neven the name of the facility she was hospitalized in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.88,0:11:44.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That would explain why they answered\Nall the questions exactly the same...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.88,0:11:47.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How can I identify which is which, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.45,0:11:51.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As I thought, there is someone out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.30,0:11:52.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.22,0:11:53.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's not just one or two of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.22,0:11:55.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.10,0:11:55.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.35,0:11:59.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The hell are we doing outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.81,0:12:02.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who's there!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.07,0:12:06.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective Takagi, and Detective Chiba?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.61,0:12:08.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you two doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.11,0:12:10.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.53,0:12:12.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're on a stakeout...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.16,0:12:17.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For the suspect from fifteen years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.33,0:12:19.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fifteen years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.79,0:12:21.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you forgotten, Mouri?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.09,0:12:26.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the one who left this scar on my face...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.59,0:12:28.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The suspect from back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.05,0:12:30.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Superintendent Matsumoto...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.72,0:12:34.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, superintendent...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.10,0:12:37.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fifteen years ago, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} had just been promoted to detective...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.14,0:12:38.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And wasn't involved in that case.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.72,0:12:40.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.02,0:12:42.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, superintendent...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.85,0:12:47.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the time I was assigned to the metropolitan\Npolice, I'm pretty sure you already had that scar...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.61,0:12:48.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.98,0:12:51.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Five years prior to that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.15,0:12:53.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That same suspect gave me this scar with a katana.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.53,0:12:55.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could you mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.62,0:12:56.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Twenty years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.58,0:12:59.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I cornered him at the docks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.87,0:13:05.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I took the katana from his hand and paid him a strike of my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.13,0:13:07.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On his body...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.50,0:13:09.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a 1-shaped scar.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.05,0:13:12.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A 1-shaped scar...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.88,0:13:14.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.80,0:13:16.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.05,0:13:18.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After seeing this woman's story on the news a few days ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.22,0:13:22.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I figured that guy would take notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.06,0:13:24.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.27,0:13:25.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.98,0:13:29.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was the scar from the katana on his chest or his back?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.32,0:13:31.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid I don't quite remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.28,0:13:34.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was certainly a worthy adversary, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.03,0:13:36.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.91,0:13:38.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You neither...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.45,0:13:40.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, at the time, the superintendent...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.83,0:13:43.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Had just been cut across his left eye, so it wasn't easy for him to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.75,0:13:47.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it seems I was right in coming here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.38,0:13:50.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This scar on my left eye...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.84,0:13:52.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's starting to ache.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.72,0:13:59.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's telling me that our man is in that house.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.44,0:14:09.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a serial killer from fifteen years ago is in this house!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.03,0:14:14.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We still aren't sure if he's actually in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.49,0:14:19.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, what Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} said earlier about us being watched...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.74,0:14:21.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.62,0:14:25.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Superintendent Matsumoto has been\Nlooking for this criminal for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.33,0:14:29.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems this was the one who gave him the scar on his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.96,0:14:32.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, at the same time, the superintendent...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.34,0:14:37.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He used that guy's katana in retaliation\Nand left a 1-shaped wound on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.76,0:14:40.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A 1-shaped wound—does that mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.93,0:14:41.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.89,0:14:45.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It would seem the serial killer has it as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.64,0:14:48.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From one side to the other, there should\Nbe a large wound from the katana.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.19,0:14:52.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, why has a serial killer come to this house?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.15,0:14:57.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's likely he has his sights set on the 100 million yen lottery ticket.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.07,0:14:59.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, he can use the scar he got from the superintendent.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.45,0:15:01.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.03,0:15:07.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The boy from her memories could be either the brown-\Nhaired Kusumoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} or the dark-skinned Banba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.75,0:15:11.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the one that isn't could be the serial killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.25,0:15:14.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.09,0:15:16.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where is the serial killer's scar?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.05,0:15:18.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think Kusumoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s scar is on his back...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.93,0:15:21.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While Banba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s is on his chest, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.43,0:15:22.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.64,0:15:25.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems the superintendent doesn't remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.52,0:15:28.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it did happen just after his eye was injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.23,0:15:31.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, do you mean to say there aren't\Nany other clues aside from the scar?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.19,0:15:34.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, the culprit then was wearing gloves...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.94,0:15:38.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which meant they couldn't lift any fingerprints\Nfrom the katana that was taken from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.11,0:15:42.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And since the katana had been the\Nmurder weapon in multiple cases...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.53,0:15:48.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The blood of the criminal and that of his victims had\Nmixed together, which made it difficult to pinpoint.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.87,0:15:50.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And he didn't see his face?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.87,0:15:51.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.75,0:15:54.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With a hat, long hair, and beard...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.13,0:15:55.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was clearly a disguise.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.76,0:15:58.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's obviously not going to be enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.59,0:16:00.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about the whistling?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.72,0:16:02.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whistling?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.51,0:16:07.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since the murderer was always whistling a certain melody...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.35,0:16:11.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Superintendent Matsumoto said, "Casually keep\Nwatch over those two and find out who is who."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.52,0:16:14.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, what kind of melody is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.52,0:16:15.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.28,0:16:20.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was reluctant to share any further information\Nwith me, and when I tried to get it out of him...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.82,0:16:25.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said it's possible that I would make it "obvious" a\Npolice investigation was ongoing, so he didn't tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.83,0:16:26.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.87,0:16:31.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If there's such a dangerous person in here, there's\Nno reason to have sent Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} back inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.37,0:16:34.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I actually had no choice but to come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.42,0:16:39.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I suddenly disappeared, the murderer might suspect something...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.05,0:16:42.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then discover the police watching over the house outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.93,0:16:44.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.51,0:16:46.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As I said before...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.06,0:16:51.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can't be 100% sure that one of those two is the murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.10,0:16:51.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.15,0:16:54.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.07,0:16:58.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The bath has been prepared, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.28,0:16:59.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Should you like...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.90,0:17:02.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Offering a bath, even after treating us to that feast...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.61,0:17:05.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, if you would be so kind!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.78,0:17:11.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there's only one washroom here, so should you wish to use it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.37,0:17:12.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perhaps the young lady should go first.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.21,0:17:15.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.42,0:17:18.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You won't be able to use a washroom at\Na place like this for a long time to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.55,0:17:20.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess so...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.30,0:17:22.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.80,0:17:24.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't we go in together?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.76,0:17:27.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's been a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.47,0:17:29.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since we washed each other's backs, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.72,0:17:32.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-No, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.10,0:17:33.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't have any clothes to change into...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.73,0:17:36.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I was just in one yesterday, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.97,0:17:37.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.98,0:17:40.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.03,0:17:44.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you really want to do it, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.24,0:17:46.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Enjoy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.54,0:17:54.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought you probably wouldn't want\Nto go, so I decided not to enter either.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.33,0:17:56.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.00,0:18:00.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I can focus on the murderer instead of the bath now...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.51,0:18:06.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, so long as we don't know which melody he\Nwhistled so often, there isn't much to go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.31,0:18:12.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First, we'll need to see through those two\Nand find out which is the boy from the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.81,0:18:15.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.60,0:18:19.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle Kogoro talked with Kusumoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and Banba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.23,0:18:21.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.03,0:18:25.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They mentioned the day of the accident and\Nthe name of the hospital she was taken to...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.40,0:18:27.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems they both relayed the same story.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.95,0:18:29.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Were they really identical?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.83,0:18:31.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not even a small difference between them?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.08,0:18:34.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know, that's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.12,0:18:36.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were there and didn't listen this one time?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.13,0:18:41.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Blame the police outside for getting my attention instead...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.84,0:18:43.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.09,0:18:44.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If only their stories differed...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.88,0:18:49.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kusumoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} claimed he was was thin as a child...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.60,0:18:53.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While Banba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} said he was always studying hard when he was young.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.31,0:18:55.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.98,0:19:00.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would you like to ask that lady yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.36,0:19:02.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.32,0:19:05.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have a feeling that she...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.57,0:19:10.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Already knows exactly which one is the one she's looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.03,0:19:13.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.20,0:19:16.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've seen these in dramas and movies, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.79,0:19:20.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To think this sort of luxurious bath exists...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.00,0:19:26.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, if it isn't Mr. Detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.09,0:19:28.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We thought we'd join you if you didn't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.59,0:19:30.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You two entering together, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.84,0:19:32.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Must be well acquainted!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.64,0:19:34.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nah, just a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.56,0:19:38.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard you were coming into the bath, so I thought I'd join you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.98,0:19:41.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And maybe see how your case is going.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.44,0:19:42.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.11,0:19:43.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.11,0:19:46.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You already know which of us is real, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.07,0:19:49.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a trade secret, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.24,0:19:51.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.82,0:19:57.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now I can ask about the melody just as the superintendent\Nrequested, but without approaching these two directly...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.96,0:20:01.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, isn't that the butler?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.79,0:20:04.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You joining us as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.42,0:20:05.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.55,0:20:09.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am only here to see to the detective's back...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.80,0:20:11.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Per request of the madam.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.64,0:20:17.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My, I believe you're suspecting too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.18,0:20:20.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I had already known which it was...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.40,0:20:23.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I would have had no reason for calling Detective Mouri here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.73,0:20:25.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess not, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.11,0:20:26.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.98,0:20:30.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is there anything from the past you omitted during the TV interview?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.16,0:20:33.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I believe I included it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.24,0:20:37.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You see, he was a perfectly honest person by nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.62,0:20:41.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I figured it would be simple for Detective Mouri to solve.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.12,0:20:43.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perfectly honest?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.75,0:20:44.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.79,0:20:49.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He bought packed sushi for lunch, and when he later\Nrealized he'd received 100 extra yen in change...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.97,0:20:52.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He went really far out of his way to return it to the shop, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.89,0:20:53.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.64,0:20:55.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said it was because it didn't belong to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.35,0:20:58.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That person liked sushi, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.77,0:20:59.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.73,0:21:02.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When we ate fried noodles in a house by the sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.90,0:21:06.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was surprised to see him heap such a\Nlarge amount of red ginger onto his plate.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.57,0:21:09.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That may be the first time I've heard that story...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.74,0:21:10.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.99,0:21:13.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, please relay that to Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.78,0:21:19.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.91,0:21:21.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, please do not bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.33,0:21:23.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.17,0:21:24.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whenever I enter a bath...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.58,0:21:27.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I feel like reciting "Hana Uta," or another great tune!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.38,0:21:28.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How about you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.71,0:21:29.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.96,0:21:31.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.67,0:21:33.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Happen to have any favorite songs?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.26,0:21:35.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.05,0:21:38.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There is a melody I find myself humming a lot, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.98,0:21:47.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Superintendent!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.19,0:21:49.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've received a mail from Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.40,0:21:51.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.24,0:21:54.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"The brown-haired guy chooses jazz...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.49,0:21:56.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"While the dark-skinned guy prefers soul."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.32,0:21:58.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.91,0:22:02.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Return a mail to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.12,0:22:04.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just say...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.37,0:22:07.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Continue the investigation," huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.54,0:22:09.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really now...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.88,0:22:12.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To order me around just when I send news...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.97,0:22:15.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Butler, you doing all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.18,0:22:16.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You have a pretty heavy sweat going.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.18,0:22:18.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.60,0:22:22.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The air conditioning in the bathroom went out not long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.98,0:22:24.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Due to the sweat, I can see...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.10,0:22:26.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A scar!?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.19,0:22:28.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.31,0:22:31.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means that, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.19,0:22:34.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The number of people with a 1-shaped scar in this house...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.40,0:22:36.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is now up to a total of three...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.74,0:24:02.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're wondering whether it's natural or manufactured?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.82,0:24:04.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.33,0:24:08.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A letter on the bodies of the victims, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.35,0:24:32.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.30,0:24:34.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sushi
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.46,0:24:35.47,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Order any sushi you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.46,0:24:39.45,Signs,,0,0,0,,Look forward to the next episode
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.48,0:24:37.73,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,All righty, let's have sea urchin,\Nabalone, tuna belly, salmon roe...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.74,0:24:39.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, two eggs.
